7
00:00:29,640 --> 00:00:30,800
You're so into me.

8
00:00:30,800 --> 00:00:32,680
Aren't you?

9
00:00:33,960 --> 00:00:34,960
Is that so wrong?

10
00:00:35,640 --> 00:00:36,760
It is, isn't it?

11
00:00:37,200 --> 00:00:38,200
Of course.

12
00:00:41,560 --> 00:00:43,200
What am I going to do?

13
00:00:46,960 --> 00:00:47,960
Ever since that moment...

14
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:56,520
What do these people
take me for?

15
00:00:58,440 --> 00:01:00,720
I may cheat,

16
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:02,680
but that doesn't mean

17
00:01:02,920 --> 00:01:04,440
you can cheat on me.

18
00:01:05,920 --> 00:01:08,160
You wretched women.

19
00:01:08,960 --> 00:01:11,360
You're nothing.

20
00:01:11,360 --> 00:01:12,760
Just a boost for my ego.

21
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:14,080
Objects for my pleasure.

22
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:16,680
I will never forgive you.

23
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:18,320
I'll make you
rot in hell.

24
00:01:18,320 --> 00:01:19,760
And you will regret everything.
